de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.common
Class HTTPXAbstractMessage

java.lang.Object
  de.fhg.fokus.restac.httpx.core.common.HTTPXAbstractMessage
Direct Known Subclasses:
HTTPXActionMessage, HTTPXStatusMessage
public abstract class HTTPXAbstractMessage
extends java.lang.Object

Stores an HTTP message as defined in RFC 2616. Subclasses are HTTPXActionMessage and HTTPXStatusMessage.

Author:
Murat Ates
See Also:
HTTPXActionMessage, HTTPXStatusMessage
